Necessary packages require for testing :

steps:

1 . npm init -y 

2.  npm install express mongoose jsonwebtoken cors bcrypt 

3. Import them ..

4. connect MongoDB Atlas with my url .

5. node index.js (will run the server at backend).

6. Use POSTMAN for testing purpose.

Note : JWT only implemented for teachers thus use teachers route only(such as : /teacher , /teacher/login , /teacher/register , /teachre/teachers-data) for this purpose .
 teacher/teachres-data is restricted only authorized to the authenticated teacher .